WEBVTT

00:05:29.667 --> 00:05:32.268
we were made to become that thing,

00:05:32.292 --> 00:05:35.851
and so we have been bred like horses,

00:05:35.875 --> 00:05:38.559
fed like turtles to alligators,

00:05:38.583 --> 00:05:40.184
branded like cattle,

00:05:40.208 --> 00:05:41.726
milked like sows,

00:05:41.750 --> 00:05:44.292
made into oxen to plow.

00:05:45.542 --> 00:05:47.684
Gender did not matter,

00:05:47.708 --> 00:05:50.143
so long as our body parts,

00:05:50.167 --> 00:05:52.726
our arms and legs and backs,

00:05:52.750 --> 00:05:54.268
our breasts and genitalia

00:05:54.292 --> 00:05:56.292
could be turned into profit.

00:05:57.917 --> 00:06:00.851
The Black body was made not white